salesforce community - adding users
"role is what you can see" : "profile is what you can do with it"

salesforce classic
accounts > new account
create individual client (or individual prospect)
Manage eternal account > Enable user > create personal account, select profile add email address, add username .  Enable options like 'Knowledge user' checkbox.  > save
Email is sent
Follow the 'contact' link.
Login to community to test the new user 'individual client' account

In Communities only - the same

